---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';

const title = 'Wanderings and Misadventures';
const description = "A site of Brooke Storm's thoughts and ramblings.";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <main class="shell">
    <section class="terminal" aria-labelledby="site-title">
      <div class="screen-label" aria-hidden="true">CROOKEDSTORM-64</div>
      <p class="eyebrow">READY.</p>
      <h1 id="site-title" class="home-title sr-only">
        Wanderings and Misadventures
      </h1>
      <pre
        class="ascii-title"
        aria-hidden="true">__        ___    _   _ ____  _____ ____  ___ _   _  ____ ____  
\ \      / / \  | \ | |  _ \| ____|  _ \|_ _| \ | |/ ___/ ___| 
 \ \ /\ / / _ \ |  \| | | | |  _| | |_) || ||  \| | |  _\___ \ 
  \ V  V / ___ \| |\  | |_| | |___|  _ &lt; | || |\  | |_| |___) |
   \_/\_/_/   \_\_| \_|____/|_____|_| \_\___|_| \_|\____|____/
    _    _   _ ____  
   / \  | \ | |  _ \ 
  / _ \ |  \| | | | |
 / ___ \| |\  | |_| |
/_/   \_\_| \_|____/ 
 __  __ ___ ____    _    ______     _______ _   _ _____ _   _ ____  _____ ____
|  \/  |_ _/ ___|  / \  |  _ \ \   / / ____| \ | |_   _| | | |  _ \| ____/ ___|
| |\/| || |\___ \ / _ \ | | | \ \ / /|  _| |  \| | | | | | | | |_) |  _| \___ \
| |  | || | ___) / ___ \| |_| |\ V / | |___| |\  | | | | |_| |  _ &lt;| |___ ___) |
|_|  |_|___|____/_/   \_\____/  \_/  |_____|_| \_| |_|  \___/|_| \_\_____|____/
      </pre>
      <p class="command-line">
        <span aria-hidden="true">LOAD</span> "THOUGHTS AND RAMBLINGS",8,1
      </p>
      <p>
        Welcome, traveler. You have found Brooke’s campfire at the edge of the
        network. The map is cluttered with homelab experiments, overland routes,
        geocache clues, photographs, and assorted misadventures.
      </p>
      <nav class="home-actions" aria-label="Main paths">
        <a class="button-link" href="/world/">Enter the World</a>
        <a class="button-link" href="/about/">About</a>
        <a class="button-link" href="/blog/">Blog</a>
        <a class="button-link" href="/projects/">Projects</a>
        <a class="button-link" href="/legacy/">Archives</a>
      </nav>
      <noscript>
        <p>
          JavaScript will eventually enable the boot sequence and interactive
          world. Content will remain available without it.
        </p>
      </noscript>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
